definitions.definition: A village in Haworth and Stanbury parish, in the City of Bradford , West Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE0337 ) .
A borough in Bergen County , New Jersey , United States .
A town in McCurtain County , Oklahoma , United States .
A habitational surname from Old English .
